9. Conclusion

This project demonstrates how digital images can be manipulated using basic operations like resizing and rotation.

It provides understanding of image matrix operations, coordinate transformations, and image display/save techniques.

Useful for preprocessing images in real-world applications such as computer vision and machine learning.




